Package: opencpu
Type: Package
Title: The OpenCPU system for embedded scientific computing and reproducible
    research.
Version: 1.4.6
Date: 2015-01-24
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: http://www.opencpu.org, http://arxiv.org/abs/1406.4806
BugReports: http://github.com/jeroenooms/opencpu/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    parallel,
    tools,
    stats,
    evaluate (>= 0.5.1),
    httpuv (>= 1.3),
    knitr (>= 1.6),
    jsonlite (>= 0.9.14),
    devtools (>= 1.6.1),
    httr (>= 0.3),
